2.2 Individual Privacy Leakage Probability
Individual Privacy Leakage Probability(IPLP) describes the probability that a user divulge his/her friends‚Äô privacy based on his/her subjective consciousness. Inspired by [7], two vectors,

81

namely privacy protection awareness(PPA) and privacy protection trust(PPT) are proposed in this paper to estimate IPLP.

