4.2.4 Experiment 4
In this experiment, 10 users are selected to evaluate the unfriending methods, which decrease the privacy disclosure probability with respect to the max degree, IPLP and RPLP of friend connections. The concrete strategies are as following:

1.Unfriend Facebook users‚Äô friend with the maximum degree.

2.Unfriend Facebook users‚Äô friend with the maximum IPLP.

3.Unfriend Facebook users‚Äô friends with maximum RPLP.

The experiment results of unfriending the user‚Äôs friend in column 1 is shown in Table 2.

